    <!-- 
    Narrative Plan:
    1. Hook: Grab attention with "Headline Statistics" to establish high stakes. Visualize key percentages with a bar chart and showcase monetary figures as large, impactful numbers.
    2. Problem & Insight: Detail the "Six Core Challenges" in a grid. Each challenge card includes a summary and a "Hidden Danger" callout to demonstrate deep expertise.
    3. Solution & Value: Present the "Strategic Paradigm Shifts" as the core value proposition, showing how our approach has evolved to meet modern demands.
    4. CTA: Conclude with a clear call to action.

    Visualization Choices:
    - Headline Statistics (Percentages): Goal: Compare. Visualization: Bar Chart (Chart.js/Canvas). Justification: Effectively compares the contribution of different factors to data center incidents. NO SVG.
    - Headline Statistics (Monetary): Goal: Inform. Visualization: Single Big Number (Styled HTML). Justification: Maximum impact for critical financial data. NO SVG.
    - Six Core Challenges: Goal: Organize. Visualization: Icon-driven cards in a grid (Styled HTML/CSS with Material Symbols Font). Justification: Clear, scannable organization of complex topics. NO SVG, NO MERMAID JS.
    - Strategic Paradigm Shifts: Goal: Organize/Compare. Visualization: Flow-style layout (Styled HTML/CSS). Justification: Visually represents the transformation from old to new thinking. NO SVG, NO MERMAID JS.

    Color Palette: "Brilliant Blues"
    - Background: #0A192F (Dark Navy)
    - Card/Element Background: #172A46 (Rich Navy)
    - Primary Text: #CCD6F6 (Light Slate)
    - Heading/Accent: #64FFDA (Vibrant Cyan)
    - Secondary Text: #8892B0 (Slate Grey)
    - Risk/Danger Accent: #EF4444 (Sharp Red)

    Confirmation: NEITHER Mermaid JS NOR SVG were used in this output. All visuals are rendered via HTML/CSS/Tailwind or the HTML5 Canvas via Chart.js.
    -->
